description:
Take a look at the official trailer for Wonder Man, the next action-adventure superhero installment in the MCU distributed by Marvel Studios. 

Hollywood actor Simon Williams is thrust into the world of superheroes as he gets powers of his own, and becomes the new superhero Wonder Man.

Wonder Man stars Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Ben Kingsley, Demetrius Grosse, Lauren Glazier, Byron Bowers, and more. The series was created by Destin Daniel Cretton.

Wonder Man premieres January 27 at 6PM PT only on Disney+

#IGN
title: Wonder Man - Official Trailer (2026) Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Ben Kingsley

author: IGN
description:
Don't miss the How To Play Conquest trailer for Battlefield 6, the latest entry in the first-person action shooter franchise developed by DICE, Battlefield Studios, and EA. Conquest is the home of iconic all-out warfare where tanks, jets, and attack helicopters turn the tides of battle. This mode often features the largest player count, and these decrease any time a player is killed without being revived. Lives also decrease due to captured objectives; for every objective under one team’s control, the other team loses one life every couple of seconds. When a team’s lives hit zero, the battle’s over. 
Battlefield 6 is available now for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam).
title: Battlefield 6 - Official How To Play Conquest Trailer

author: IGN
description:
You’ve finished Ghost of Yotei… now what? Is there a New Game Plus mode? Can you keep exploring Ezo after the main story? And does the world itself change once Atsu’s journey comes to an end? In this video, Erica Alatorre from IGN’s video guides team breaks down everything Ghost of Yotei has to offer after the credits roll – all without spoiling the main story.

From post-game world events and bounty hunter encounters to secret animal sanctuaries and Shamisen songs that help with trophy hunting, we’ll show you everything that unlocks after the finale and how to make the most of your time in Ezo. We’ll also walk you through the chase for Platinum – including tips on finding shrines, hot springs, and puzzle boxes, and how to make the most of the guiding wind to track down everything you missed.
title: Ghost of Yotei Post-Game Guide: Endgame, NG+, and What to Do After the Credits
